{"tid":1796824,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"前輩練志偉2002年示範如何正確地向散仔打氣 － 「Happy New Year」","createTime":"2019-12-25T01:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T14:57:11.000Z","uid":39092,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb000c879e7b694b1d52401daa5b2e93e665626","tid":1796824,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:58:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25A8%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAYxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=b1e05376\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a><br />\n<br />\n新年快樂事件是香港2002年元旦發生的一件警民衝突事件，事發地點為九龍尖沙咀近香港文化中心一帶的跨年倒數活動，一名14歲青年練志偉與一名警員互相掌摑，其後該名青年投訴被一名警員毆打，而警方則回應指<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只是二人互相輕拍面部並向對方祝賀「Happy New Year」</span></span>（新年快樂）。經過警方內部調查後，投訴警方獨立監察委員會最後接納警方的調查報告，指未能證實青年曾被毆打，只能證實雙方曾經講過粗口，所以終止調查工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/192904_838a2c6084bc9abea1e9055a038bac67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F192904_838a2c6084bc9abea1e9055a038bac67.jpg&h=73391575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=325774471598386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D325774471598386&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAYxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=3b720059\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=325774471598386</a><br />\n<br />\nhappy new year <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ced3d5cb169c5d4b71052e893b3b13b0748c97","tid":1796824,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35a821584d302d95d790c551e3369147cad8646","tid":1796824,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:18:06.000Z","msg":"只能證實雙方曾經講過粗口<br />\n<br />\n公職人員執勤期間講粗口都夠嚴重啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b1835c25fefe3fd7f3f66a03aedb1d247b0a32","tid":1796824,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"元旦行動代號：Happy New Year"},{"pid":"b87fa38837be7124611b90c01d3b91a014b1db5b","tid":1796824,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"當年市民同警察互冚 警隊為咗保住個老散<br />\n竟然高層出黎高調幫個市民作埋個咁灰諧嘅下台階 但求息事寧人 <br />\n<br />\n今時今日同打一單嘢嘅話 <br />\n應該隻冚人前綫狗會開咗實彈射中個市民<br />\n再搵十幾隻防暴狗守住間病房 等佢喺ICU出返黎之後告暴動加襲警 <br />\n而隻冚人狗就會接受央視訪問 講述被冚後身心嚴重受創黎緊要請成年工傷假嘅慘況 然後黨企就送間大灣區千呎豪宅作以慰問 到下年71就拎埋金英勇勳章 <br />\n<br />\n點解警隊民望低撚到咁 其實原因就係咁簡單架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da6b57a7728c294765fb9777c0bb20057db57ae","tid":1796824,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"集體回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f55c1557847963688405fbcceb3b724e6a8ce6","tid":1796824,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:57:11.000Z","msg":"今年32歲的練志偉唔知過成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}